function onChange(control, oldValue, newValue, isLoading) {
	if (isLoading || newValue == '') {
		return;
	}
	
	//Get value from script include
	var ga = new GlideAjax('OCIO_SR_HelperUtils');
	ga.addParam('sysparm_name', 'ajaxFtn_getUserById');
	ga.addParam('sysparm_src_sysid',  newValue);
	ga.getXMLAnswer(cbFtn);
	function cbFtn(answer) {
		if (answer) {
			var retObj = JSON.parse(answer);

	
			g_form.setValue('u_organization', retObj.company, retObj.company);
			
			
					
		}
	}
	
}]]></script><sys_class_name>catalog_script_client</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>MKURIAKOSE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-09-20 19:28:02</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>cf15a52bdbe4ab4050479eb6db961980</sys_id><sys_mod_count>3</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Set Default from Requested For</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>catalog_script_client_cf15a52bdbe4ab4050479eb6db961980</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>MKURIAKOSE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-10-06 01:45:38</sys_updated_on><table/><type>onChange</type><ui_type>10</ui_type><variable_set/><view/></catalog_script_client></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.OCIO_SR_Call_Record_Details</api_name><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>OCIO_SR_Call_Record_Details</name><script><![CDATA[var OCIO_SR_Call_Record_Details = Class.create();
OCIO_SR_Call_Record_Details.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	
//Populate Call record details to the catalog for New calls. Its called by Client scripts from 
	
	   call_info: function() {
		var CallRecord = this.getParameter('sysparam_CallRecord');
		var result = this.newItem("result");
		var call_details = new GlideRecord('new_call');
		call_details.addQuery('sys_id',CallRecord);
		call_details.query();
		if(call_details.next())
			{
			    result.setAttribute("call_short_desc",call_details.short_description);
			    result.setAttribute("call_req_for", call_details.u_requested_for);
				result.setAttribute("call_req_by", call_details.caller);
				result.setAttribute("call_im_req_for", call_details.company);
				result.setAttribute("call_description", call_details.description);


				
			}
	},

	
    type: 'OCIO_SR_Call_Record_Details'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>MKURIAKOSE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-09-20 22:00:34</sys_created_on><sys_id>acb78223db68ab4050479eb6db9619b5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>19</sys_mod_count><sys_name>OCIO_SR_Call_Record_Details</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_acb78223db68ab4050479eb6db9619b5</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>MKURIAKOSE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-10-06 01:49:06</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="catalog_script_client"><catalog_script_client action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><applies_catalog>true</applies_catalog><applies_extended>false</applies_extended><applies_req_item>false</applies_req_item><applies_sc_task>false</applies_sc_task><applies_target_record>false</applies_target_record><applies_to>item</applies_to><cat_item display_value="General Service Request">be15a52bdbe4ab4050479eb6db961928</cat_item><cat_variable/><condition/><description/><field/><global>true</global><messages/><name>Get Call record data on load</name><order/><script><![CDATA[function onLoad() {


var call_record = getParmVal('sysparm_call_record');
var ga = new GlideAjax("OCIO_SR_Call_Record_Details");
ga.addParam("sysparm_name","call_info");
ga.addParam("sysparam_CallRecord",call_record);
ga.getXML(ajaxResponse);	
  
}

function getParmVal(name){
    var url = document.URL.parseQuery();
    if(url[name]){
        return decodeURI(url[name]);
    }
    else{
        return;
    }
}	

	function ajaxResponse(serverResponse) {
	var result = serverResponse.responseXML.getElementsByTagName("result");
	var call_req_for = result[0].getAttribute("call_req_for");
	var call_req_by = result[0].getAttribute("call_req_by");
	var call_short_desc=result[0].getAttribute("call_short_desc");
	var call_im_req_for= result[0].getAttribute("call_im_req_for");
	var call_description= result[0].getAttribute("call_description");
		
		
	g_form.setValue('u_requested_for',call_req_for);
	g_form.setValue('Short_Description',call_short_desc);
	g_form.setValue('u_requested_by',call_req_by);
	g_form.setValue('u_organization',call_im_req_for);
	g_form.setValue('Description',call_description);	
			

	}
	
   
]]></script><sys_class_name>catalog_script_client</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>MKURIAKOSE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-09-20 21:05:24</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>f44b75e7db28ab4050479eb6db96193a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>26</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Get Call record data on load</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>catalog_script_client_f44b75e7db28ab4050479eb6db96193a</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>MKURIAKOSE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-10-06 01:47:19</sys_updated_on><table/><type>onLoad</type><ui_type>10</ui_type><variable_set/><view/></catalog_script_client></record_update>
